todos.task: Drink a cup of coffee to kickstart your day.
Finish the online course you've been working on.
Take a contrast shower to refresh and energize yourself.
Schedule time to read at least one chapter of a book you've been meaning to start. Setting aside even 15 minutes a day can help you build a solid reading habit.
Organize your workspace by decluttering and arranging everything neatly, so you can focus better and be more productive throughout the day. A tidy space always boosts concentration and creativity
